#[[favor|Favored]] by [[hap]], [[luck]], or [[fortune]]; [[lucky]]; [[fortunate]]; [[successful]]; [[prosperous]]; [[satisfy]]ing [[desire]].
#:''a happy expedient''
#:''a happy effort''
#:''a happy venture''
